author: ekoneil
msg: Change the name of the "pagerStyle" attribute on the <netui-data:configurePager> tag to "pagerFormat".
This seemed to be confusing because the "Style" attributes are usually reserved for CSS styles -- not output formats.

author: dain
msg: Changed all module builders to not work directly with document objects

prevents lots fo extra complexity in the deployment code
